messages.message: What happened to AI Hub Docs chatbot? I am in important demos and things keep changing unexpectedly. I opened Ask Trust bot and that is broken too. Can we please ensure that our official chatbots remains stable and reliable. This is not good.

AIHub docs chatbot is available now. For the newer version of the chatbot, we need to set the visibility manually. Auto setting the visibility will be available from 24.38 release.

I am able to query the Ask Trust bot (https://aihub.instabase.com/hub/apps/6e6af2ba-c695-4067-9603-171dab2258c8). Can you please add more details here?

cc: @avi
